<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <% include ../partials/head %>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <% include ../partials/navbar %>

    <div class="container-fluid text-uppercase fixed-bottom pt-3 op-80">
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-end">
            <div class="col-sm-5">
                <% include ../partials/alerts %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid p-4 main-home background-red text-light" id="home">

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-sm-8 text-center text-uppercase">
                    <h1 class="content-title">Restaurante Universitário</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-8">
                    <p class="px-4 pt-4 text-justify">
                        O Restaurante Universitário proporciona à comunidade universitária espaço de convivência,
                        integrando as ações
                        de educação, formação profissional, saúde, alimentação e lazer. Atende diariamente a 1400
                        comensais com almoço e jantar. As vagas disponíveis para almoço destinam-se a estudantes
                        regularmente matriculados e frequentes nos cursos de graduação da UFAL, observando-se as normas
                        estabelecidas nas resoluções vigentes. O jantar é oferecido para toda a comunidade acadêmica.
                    </p>
                    <p class="px-4 pb-4 text-justify">
                        Você pode entrar de maneira simples e rápida em nosso site, aproveitando assim das
                        comodidades e praticidades de pagar suas refeições de maneira eletrônica.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
                    <a href="/auth" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg sans-13 px-4 text-uppercase">Entrar Agora</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid bg-light" id="menu">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row text-center text-uppercase mb-3">
                <p class="h1 w-100 content-title">
                    Cardápio<br>Semanal
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="list-group" id="list-tab" role="tablist">
                        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between active" id="list-monday" data-toggle="list"
                            href="#list-tab-monday" role="tab" aria-controls="home">
                            Segunda
                            
                            <small class="small-day"><%= locals.menu.days[1].date.day %>/<%= locals.menu.days[1].date.month %>/<%= locals.menu.days[1].date.year %></small>
                        </a>
                        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between" id="list-tuesday" data-toggle="list"
                            href="#list-tab-tuesday" role="tab" aria-controls="profile">
                            Terça

                            <small class="small-day"><%= locals.menu.days[2].date.day %>/<%= locals.menu.days[2].date.month %>/<%= locals.menu.days[2].date.year %></small>
                        </a>
                        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between" id="list-wednesday" data-toggle="list"
                            href="#list-tab-wednesday" role="tab" aria-controls="messages">
                            Quarta

                            <small class="small-day"><%= locals.menu.days[3].date.day %>/<%= locals.menu.days[3].date.month %>/<%= locals.menu.days[3].date.year %></small>
                        </a>
                        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between" id="list-thursday" data-toggle="list"
                            href="#list-tab-thursday" role="tab" aria-controls="settings">
                            Quinta

                            <small class="small-day"><%= locals.menu.days[4].date.day %>/<%= locals.menu.days[4].date.month %>/<%= locals.menu.days[4].date.year %></small>
                        </a>
                        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between" id="list-thursday" data-toggle="list"
                            href="#list-tab-friday" role="tab" aria-controls="settings">
                            Sexta

                            <small class="small-day"><%= locals.menu.days[5].date.day %>/<%= locals.menu.days[5].date.month %>/<%= locals.menu.days[5].date.year %></small>
                        </a>
                        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between" id="list-thursday" data-toggle="list"
                            href="#list-tab-saturday" role="tab" aria-controls="settings">
                            Sábado

                            <small class="small-day"><%= locals.menu.days[6].date.day %>/<%= locals.menu.days[6].date.month %>/<%= locals.menu.days[6].date.year %></small>
                        </a>
                        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between" id="list-thursday" data-toggle="list"
                            href="#list-tab-sunday" role="tab" aria-controls="settings">
                            Domingo

                            <small class="small-day"><%= locals.menu.days[0].date.day %>/<%= locals.menu.days[0].date.month %>/<%= locals.menu.days[0].date.year %></small>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-8">
                    <div class="tab-content" id="nav-tabContent">
                        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="list-tab-monday" role="tabpanel"
                            aria-labelledby="list-home-list">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                                        <dl class="p-4">
                                            <dt>Almoço</dt>
                                            
                                            <dl>
                                                <dt>Carnes</dt>
                                                <% locals.menu.days[1].lunch.meat.forEach(meat => { %>
                                                    <dd><%= meat.name %></dd>
                                                <% }) %>
                                            </dl>
                                            
                                            <dl>
                                                <dt>Pratos Vegetariano</dt>
                                                <% locals.menu.days[1].lunch.vegetarian.forEach(vegie => { %>
                                                    <dd><%= vegie.name %></dd>
                                                <% }) %>
                                            </dl>
                                            
                                            <dl>
                                                <dt>Acompanhamentos</dt>
                                                <% locals.menu.days[1].lunch.sideDish.forEach(sideDish => { %>
                                                    <dd><%= sideDish.name %></dd>
                                                <% }) %>
                                            </dl>
                                            
                                            <dl>
                                                <dt>Sobremesas</dt>
                                                <% locals.menu.days[1].lunch.dessert.forEach(dessert => { %>
                                                    <dd><%= dessert.name %></dd>
                                                <% }) %>
                                            </dl>
                                            
                                            <dl>
                                                <dt>Bebidas</dt>
                                                <% locals.menu.days[1].lunch.drinks.forEach(drink => { %>
                                                    <dd><%= drink.name %></dd>
                                                <% }) %>
                                            </dl>
                                        </dl>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-tab-tuesday" role="tabpanel"
                            aria-labelledby="list-profile-list">
                            Terça
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-tab-wednesday" role="tabpanel"
                            aria-labelledby="list-messages-list">
                            Quarta
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-tab-thursday" role="tabpanel"
                            aria-labelledby="list-settings-list">
                            Quinta
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-tab-friday" role="tabpanel"
                            aria-labelledby="list-settings-list">
                            Sexta
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-tab-saturday" role="tabpanel"
                            aria-labelledby="list-settings-list">
                            Sábado
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-tab-sunday" role="tabpanel"
                            aria-labelledby="list-settings-list">
                            Domingo
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <% include ../partials/footer %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/home.js"></script>
</body>

</html>